Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:38.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So she merged with multiple copies of her consciousness at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:39.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:47.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You did the best job you could as the front's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:49.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got us through the most dangerous situation we've been in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:57.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And nobody anticipated that she'd create all those clones and lie in wait for us in Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was Kanade's—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruthless Kanade's plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:08.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Kanade, so I don't think we could have done anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:24.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me that no one gets sick so there's no hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you wake up then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:35.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This has never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time Angel has been in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:51.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the circumstances, it's entirely possible that she won't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, given how irregular this is, she'll definitely wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:03:00.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At some point she'll wake up, and it'll be like she just overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And who will she be when she wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina talked!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This must a very, {\i1}very{\i0} serious problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:09.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, which Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:18.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the first Angel, the one who went fishing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:22.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the clones which attacked us were all aggressive and ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there were about 100 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is she unconscious now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:34.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All those minds must be fighting in her little head and kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,getting mixed up, making it really bad for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:42.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So if she wakes up, will she retain the minds of those other 100?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:47.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just going by the ratio, the chances of her waking up as her old self are about 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dealing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:56.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Takeyama to the Angel Area, along with someone who can translate the manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are TK and Matsushita?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on lookout duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:05.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So TK's useless at English after all, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:12.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to delete all the data, change the login password, and seal all her abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a temporary solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our defenses will be broken through eventually, and she'll re{\fnNyala}-{\fn}input the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just destroy the whole machine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The machine just came from the computer room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Same with the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:34.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems quite smart today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do now is entrust things to fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will God side with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:16.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap, I missed the university entrance exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little light headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your forehead's bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel faint?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nauseous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:10.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:11.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:12.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:23.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:36.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we have to get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:40.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's save anyone left inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:46.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:47.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still a little unsteady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Igarashi's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:54.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get out, I'll go get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:50.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely come back, so I'm borrowing the flashlight for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:26.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The tunnel is blocked by rubble both in front of us and behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:19.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phones have no signal and we can't contact anyone outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:24.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to work together on this, so please don't try to do anything alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's collect any food supplies and water left and share it out evenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when were you in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else can give instructions for medical care?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy knows medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you intend to abandon the wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:45.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Help will definitely arrive, so we just have to hold out till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay in this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if you're thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll tell you when it's time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who feels sick, call Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we for food?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a few packed lunches and some candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:32.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For liquids, we only have 5 or 6 bottles of water and a bottle of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days at best...{強めの「以て」と推定して・・・}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really are something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:39.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aiming to do humanitarian work abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't really planning to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:51.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just joking, don't take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But take care of yourself too or you'll be the first to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:55.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:02.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:05.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:08.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:09.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:19.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Mr. Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna tie me up or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's getting out of here alive anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You all know that, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him off! {it's 奇麗事}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid just wasted precious water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my share just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't drink any from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:42.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:46.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone punch him, I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, we'll deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'll share my portion with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:54.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:55.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's move this guy somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:00.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You, help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:06.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:07.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:57.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have I been working so hard since that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:12.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl taught me the meaning to my life for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:17.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, here I am, unable to save a single person again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stayed just as powerless as I was from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:28.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:30.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:52.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't have you catching a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you're not getting any better though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't find a donor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Donor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Igarashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a pen on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:05.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:09.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess with this, even if we die,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,our lives can still be used to help someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll give us a reason to have lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:52.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the face of despair, everyone's entrusting their hopes to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:57.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've given meaning to our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:39.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a formidable fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:43.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:48.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle that the me you made the promise with woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I remember everything now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,about how I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:06.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The train I was on when I was going to the exam center got into an accident. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to live for someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,to have people say "thank you" to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:20.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With that goal in mind, I frantically studied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:29.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I was able to leave something behind by registering as a donor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have been able to save someone with this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:47.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that person will say "thank you"\N to you for the rest of their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you don't have any more regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was able to save someone, I guess my life wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'm going to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have no more regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:23.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to remain with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're my friends, so I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:33.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I feel another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:41.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If they could feel at peace like me, and say goodbye to this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:44.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe living a new life wouldn't be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:46.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:56.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you trying to lead everyone down this path from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we first met, you stabbed me out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:05.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you told me to prove that you wouldn't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:11.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has the Battlefront been running around in circles with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's beyond a little awkward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you participate seriously in class, you'll end up happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will taking part in club activities bring you satisfaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:25.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone comes here because they weren't able to have a happy youth, after all. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:32.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to figure that out in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell just by looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is where the souls of young people come to find peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:49.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Hinata had caught that fly to second, he would have found peace and disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:54.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What meddlesome idiots we were, me and Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:59.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasawa found peace with her own strength and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is here because they want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just fighting against an unfair life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanade said that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:12.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted us to know a life which isn't unfair.{She wanted to show everyone a life without unfairness,}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to let us spend time as a normal youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to persuade those who wanted to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How ironic is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:28.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all so simple, but both sides fought for their own beliefs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,eventually even making weapons...{yagate buki made tsukuridashite}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, every day is a battle.{ima ja, 抗争 no mainichi da}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:39.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are ridiculously awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:40.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:43.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,with you here, it might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really have no regrets then you should have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:57.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the first person who could be your ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't your true regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:10.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:16.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet on that day, even with my confidence as an older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,everything I wanted to protect was stolen from me within the space of 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:22.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could it be that unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:26.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:36.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely because I don't want her to have to carry those memories forever that I want to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this clumsy Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:43.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't count on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:47.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if I don't try, the fighting will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:49.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:56.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As her friend, as the only ally she has, shouldn't I do everything I can to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:00.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:03.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't I be saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:07.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:15.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help them graduate from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:16.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:29.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we discovered that someone switched the papers for all subjects in order to make Tachibana fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:41.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After analyzing the handwriting, we declare Tachibana innocent, and reinstate her to the position of student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:47.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Naoi, who has been working hard as the acting president, will be the vice{\fnNyala}-{\fn}president again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:52.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, why do I have to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:54.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exposing all of us like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:56.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did we all get shot down in flames like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.24,0:22:58.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We agree on something for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:04.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People who've been trodden on together understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're shot{\fnNyala}-{\fn}down{\fnNyala}-{\fn}plane comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, are you trying to undress me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:11.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, go on, take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, you're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that? Stop that, it's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:16.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:22.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it looks like Angel's lost all her memories with us these last few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:23.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The 100 Angels, the ones who attacked us, appear to have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:30.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I seriously thought for a moment she could be our friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:32.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:38.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First I'll have to find out about their pasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:44.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But without an opponent, there'll be nothing to distract Yuri so I have time to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:47.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kanade, I want you to become the student council president again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.43,0:23:50.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to fight once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:53.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I need you to act as I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:56.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That plan suits me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:59.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you'll have to be alone again...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:02.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when it's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:04.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:07.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:10.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:12.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,what'll happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:19.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The band died because of your guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:19.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:22.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,German Suplex.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:22.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this one thing I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:22.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:23.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was his idiocy cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.59,0:24:24.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Us guys will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.59,0:24:25.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, whose side are you on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.94,0:24:25.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll grant that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.82,0:24:28.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All happiness was stolen from me.
