Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.76,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}When I pass through the door of the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:46.35,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I puff my chest out with a little bit of pride
